          "rationale": "Texas law requires each individual who works as an unarmed (noncommissioned) security officer for a guard company to hold an individual license from DPS and be employed by a licensed company (Tex. Occ. Code 1702.221). Completion of DPS Level II training is a prerequisite (37 TAC 35.141); the credential term is up to two years (1702.301).",
